chata / chatall               Sends a message to all chat contacts
 
   Format:
      ;chata <text>           Sends the <text> to everyone
 
   Notes:
      The Chat task is used to chat with other players directly via telnet.
         Calls can be placed (or accepted) with any user whose MUD client uses
         the zChat or MudMaster protocols.
      This command is the equivalent of typing ';chatall <text>' in any Chat
         task window.
 
   User commands:
      chata / chatall
